{"tid":2192452,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"李孝利在老公的手機裡發現娜璉的舞蹈影片","createTime":"2020-09-07T06:35:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T14:40:05.000Z","uid":222155,"like":9,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"5f1c5bc328451e17f501d0e68369095076a2d956","tid":2192452,"uid":222155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T06:35:09.000Z","msg":"一查一個準？！李尚順偷搜女愛豆被李孝利抓包：歐巴～你為什麼搜她倆<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/129705\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.koreastardaily.com%2Ftc%2Fnews%2F129705&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNp0cGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=88f866a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/129705</a><br />\n<br />\n歌壇大姐大李孝利在老公面前完全就是小女人心態，翻看老公手機之後忍不住嫉妒心大爆發。<br />\n<br />\n網路綜藝《FACE ID》9月1日首公開，預告片中李尚順李孝利夫婦之間的奇妙氣流引發所有人的關注。 原來是李孝利做了很多女生都做過的事，查了老公的手機，沒想到真的查到了李尚順的某些小秘密。<br />\n<br />\n李孝利一邊查看李尚順手機裡他常用的APP、SNS推薦影片、搜索詞等，一邊說「歐巴，你被抓住了吧」。原來是李孝利在老公的手機裡發現推送了韶宥、TWICE娜璉的舞蹈影片，她問道：「歐巴為什麼搜韶宥，為什麼歐巴會推送TWICE娜璉的西瓜舞？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oZmpfxy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoZmpfxy.gif&h=b9b2ff4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽到老婆的「質問」，原本表情泰然的李尚順神色突變，露出了緊張的神情，眼珠不停轉動，想說話又不敢說話，心虛模樣的看得人忍俊不禁。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A03Spq1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA03Spq1.gif&h=3dbe9004&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《FACE ID》是一檔明星們通過智慧手機公開日常生活的真人綜藝節目，首期嘉賓就是李尚順、李孝利夫婦。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gWpoYFYGwL4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FgWpoYFYGwL4&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNp0cGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=d6177ce7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gWpoYFYGwL4</a>"},{"pid":"8f9ade996e927546355bf2883157d495f263663e","tid":2192452,"uid":34071,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T06:38:00.000Z","msg":"見印家軍今日形勢有d不妙就推閪女人<br />\n樓主sick玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95aa1578ca1589833ed735d38d1986b730e1feed","tid":2192452,"uid":310700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T06:40:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c46ff920e28e807d5daf39fa00801e7694b641d8","tid":2192452,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T06:41:19.000Z","msg":"唔掂"},{"pid":"73e3d57a2f6642d97a9e4bf10bdea717657f41db","tid":2192452,"uid":222155,"like":5,"dislike":27,"score":-22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T06:43:44.000Z","msg":"屌，頭先張gif唔sick郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/2020-06-12-23-50-22vdPTPbJV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2F2020-06-12-23-50-22vdPTPbJV.gif&h=0752835f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f5e70008b640652e845eb169293b2832d17b5fbf","tid":2192452,"uid":37146,"like":8,"dislike":17,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T06:56:19.000Z","msg":"痴撚線，對得多老女人<br />\n想係電話收埋年輕靚女既跳舞片打個Ｊ都唔得"},{"pid":"c06b68a1ac5ce998f2c23d9c0e139a126113bdff","tid":2192452,"uid":241764,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T06:59:30.000Z","msg":"咁撚樣衰"},{"pid":"2bda541ed35ec0510d583a0a7d8c277a237f5072","tid":2192452,"uid":132174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8f9ade996e927546355bf2883157d495f263663e","tid":2192452,"uid":34071,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T06:38:00.000Z","msg":"見印家軍今日形勢有d不妙就推閪女人<br />\n樓主sick玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T07:01:10.000Z","msg":"樓主都係印家軍"},{"pid":"7d4a88e7e140922ef98c8ba5cc1549ea1d09d85f","tid":2192452,"ui